{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Crawler","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Glossary/Crawler","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary\">MDN Web Docs Glossary</a>\n\n  <ol>\n   <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Search_engine\">Search engine <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Ein Crawler ist ein Programm – oft auch Bot oder Robot genannt&nbsp;–, das systematisch das&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/World_Wide_Web\">Web <small>(en-US)</small></a> durchforstet, um Daten von Webseiten zu sammeln. Typischerweise nutzen Suchmaschinen (beispielsweise Google, Bing, etc.) Crawler zur Indexierung.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mehr_dazu","title":"Mehr dazu","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a title=\"Webcrawler\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Webcrawler\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Webcrawler</a> auf Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Mehr dazu","id":"mehr_dazu"}],"summary":"Ein Crawler ist ein Programm – oft auch Bot oder Robot genannt –, das systematisch das Web (en-US) durchforstet, um Daten von Webseiten zu sammeln. Typischerweise nutzen Suchmaschinen (beispielsweise Google, Bing, etc.) Crawler zur Indexierung.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Crawler","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Robot d'indexation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Crawler (クローラー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Crawler","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Crawler","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Crawler","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/glossary/crawler","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/glossary/crawler/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossar"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary/Crawler","title":"Crawler"}],"pageTitle":"Crawler - Glossar | MDN","noIndexing":false}}